reviewText: I love the ending of the movie when you see both women.
By Design is a funny film with a modern twist. Patty Duke is a fashion designer who wants to become a mother. A film not for the kids, but anyone with an open mind can enjoy this.
this is a not too bad comedy from a great director and a mish mash of american and canadian actors....the funniest part of the whole movie though is the guy who walks into the glass  storefront....
